<p>Zerodha offers to open<strong> a Demat account only for minors on special requests by the guardian who already has an account with Zerodha</strong>. You can open the account to hold the shares that are received by the minor as a gift or through IPO or from the guardian. You cannot sell shares or trade through the minor's account in Zerodha.</p>
